          <text><![CDATA[<p><b style=""></b><b style="">Restoring Education And Learning Act of 2018 or the REAL Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to restore Pell Grant eligibility for individuals incarcerated in a federal or state penal institution and for sex offenders subject to civil commitment following incarceration. </p>]]></text>
